Zama Adelaide Khumalo (a mụrụ n'afọ 2002) bụ onye South Africa na-agụ egwu

A maara ya nke ọma maka mmeri nke oge nke iri na isii nke South African Idols n'afọ 2020. A mụrụ ya na Witbank, Zama bịanyere aka na nkwekọrịta ndekọ nke Kalawa Jazmee, o wepụtara abọm studio mbụ In The Beginning (2021).

N'oge na-adịghị anya mgbe o meriri asọmpi ahụ, Zama malitere ịrụ ọrụ na abọm studio mbụ ya In The Beginning nke e mechara wepụta n'ọnwa Nọvemba afọ 2021. N'abalị iri na itoolu nke ọnwa Ọktọba , ewepụtara egwu ya "Is'thunzi" dị ka egwu mbụ nke abọm.
